essentials.afk.message.Description: Allow access to settings an afk message.

essentials.afk.others.Description: Allows you to AFK other players.

essentials.back.ondeath.Description: Give this permission to allow players to use /back to go to their death spot

essentials.balance.others.Description: Allows you to see the balance of other players

essentials.balancetop.force.Description: Allow a forced refresh of balancetop with "/balancetop force"

essentials.ban.exempt.Description: Prevents a specified group or player from being banned

essentials.ban.offline.Description: Allows banning of players who are offline.  This may allow you to ban exempt players.

essentials.book.author.Description: Allows the user to change the author of a book.

essentials.book.others.Description: Allow editing a book belonging to another player.

essentials.book.title.Description: Allows the user to change the title of a written book

essentials.build.Description: Allows people to build when using permission systems which don't support build toggles.

essentials.chat.ignoreexempt.Description: Someone with this permission will not be ignored, even if they are on another persons ignore list.

essentials.chat.spy.Description: A permission designed for admins, to intercept all local messages (ignoring the chat-radius).

essentials.chat.spy.exempt.Description: Allow to be exempt from chat spy

essentials.clearinventory.all.Description: Allows a player to clear all players inventories.

essentials.customtext.Description: Allow access to the /customtext command and all aliases.

essentials.delhome.others.Description: Allows you to delete the homes of other players.

essentials.eco.loan.Description: Allows the player to have a negative balance.

essentials.enderchest.others.Description: Allows you to see the contents of another players enderchest.

essentials.exp.give.Description: Allows players to give themselves exp.

essentials.exp.others.Description: Allows players to see another players exp.

essentials.feed.others.Description: Allows a player to feed another player.

essentials.gamemode.others.Description: Allows you to change the gamemode of other players.

essentials.geoip.hide.Description: Allows you to hide your country and city from people who have permission essentials.geoip.show

essentials.getpos.others.Description: Allow user to get the position of another player.

essentials.god.pvp.Description: Allows you to attack other players while in god mode.

essentials.helpop.receive.Description: Allows you to see Helpop messages

essentials.home.bed.Description: Allow access to the vanilla bed home.

essentials.home.others.Description: Allows you to teleport to homes of other players

essentials.invsee.equip.Description: Allow access to see someones equiped armor slots in "/invsee <name> [armor]"
